such a character through whom I could create a story within the genre, and Sung Min-chan, a pastor of a new church, was born.”</p><h2> Who is in the cast of the new Netflix film?</h2><p> <em>Revelations</em> will star <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-8-show"><em>The 8 Show</em></a> actor Ryu Jun-yeol as pastor Sung Min-chan. It will also feature <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/hospital-playlist">Hospital Playlist</a></em> &#39;s Shin Hyun-been as detective Lee Yeon-hui and <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/parasyte-the-grey">Parasyte: The Grey</a></em> &#39;s Shin Min-jae, who will play Kwon Yang-rae.</p><p> “Ryu Jun-yeol is an actor with exceptional acting skills,” Yeon said. “After working with him for this film, I got the feeling that this skill is based not on intuitive methodology but on a deep understanding of the work.”</p><p> “Shin Hyun-been&#39;s Lee Yeon-hui is a tragic figure,” screenwriter Choi Gyu-seok said. “Lee Yeon-hui in the comic was sharp and stoic, but in the film, she is imbued with sadness that could crush her at any moment. Shin Min-jae&#39;s Kwon Yang-rae seems like someone who just emerged from the fires of hell.”</p><p> Joining the film as an executive producer is Oscar-winning Alfonso Cuarón, previously known for his work on <em>Gravity</em> and <em>Roma.</em></p><h2> Is there a trailer for Netflix&#39;s <em>Revelations</em> ?</h2><p> The streamer dropped a tense new teaser for the upcoming film on February 24. The clip begins with the news of young Shin A-yeong going missing reaching the pastor, who happens to be a regular churchgoer. He chances upon a new member at the church, who he later finds out is Kwon Yang-rae, A-yeong&#39;s aggressor. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Revelations |官方预告片| Netflix [Eng Sub]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zLtK2ilJaJ4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2> How do I watch <em>Revelations</em> ?</h2><p> The highly anticipated new Netflix film is slated to premiere on the platform on March 21.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/revelations-netflix-korean-film-ryu-jun-yeol-3840606">Watch the intense teaser for Netflix&#39;s &#39;Revelations&#39;, starring Ryu Jun-yeol</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
